		"description": "<p>This ring has 3 charges, and it regains 1d3 expended charges daily at dawn. While wearing the ring, you can use an action to expend 1 of its charges to cast one of the following spells:</p><ul><li>@Compendium[dnd5e.spells.hDOENzjuj5WpLq7B]{Animal Friendship} (save DC 13)</li><li>@Compendium[dnd5e.spells.XXUDGFELgoskdOD0]{Fear} (save DC 13), targeting only beasts that have an Intelligence of 3 or lower</li><li>@Compendium[dnd5e.spells.aL1F8fvYLtNzUbKu]{Speak with Animals}</li></ul>",
